<p>Up until a fletching skill of 202, you can buy all your fletching components in PoK, at the east building near the DE vendor. After that, you'll have to start farming. Most Rangers perfer to Make Luclin Arrows, they're supposed to be the easiest.  <br /> <br />As far as farming for cash, EF Mammoths is your best bet for your level. Another good way, althought on Luclin, LDoN's are hardly done anymore--Mistmoore adv's used to have a nice split rate. </p>
