<p> <br />HGs in Rathe drop a decent amount of plat (up to 40pp) and FS weapons to boot. I have easily kited HGs there with a 35 druid. Problem is that ya gotta hit the zone at the right time. On Stromm at least it's more common than not to see the zone monopolized by high level toons (50-60+ or Anon) grabbing the spawns as soon as they pop. If you can avoid the underachievers you can turn a nice bit of coin there. <br /> <br /></p>
